</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='15339' id='t-15339'>Now, this is a rear-projected
drafting table.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18038' id='t-18038'>It's about 36 inches wide</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='19284' id='t-19284'>and it's equipped
with a multi-touch sensor.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='21391' id='t-21391'>Normal touch sensors that you see,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23059' id='t-23059'>like on a kiosk
or interactive whiteboards,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='25220' id='t-25220'>can only register one point
of contact at a time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='28137' id='t-28137'>This thing allows you to have
multiple points at the same time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='31876' id='t-31876'>They can use both my hands;
I can use chording actions;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35214' id='t-35214'>I can just go right up and use
all 10 fingers if I wanted to.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='38597' id='t-38597'>You know, like that.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='39778' id='t-39778'>Now, multi-touch sensing
isn't completely new.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='44345' id='t-44345'>People like Bill Buxton have been
playing around with it in the '80s.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47622' id='t-47622'>However, the approach I built here
is actually high-resolution,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='51674' id='t-51674'>low-cost, and probably
most importantly, very scalable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='55000' id='t-55000'>So, the technology, you know,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='57361' id='t-57361'>isn't the most exciting thing
here right now,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='59831' id='t-59831'>other than probably
its newfound accessibility.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62173' id='t-62173'>What's really interesting here
is what you can do with it</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='65722' id='t-65722'>and the kind of interfaces
you can build on top of it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='69141' id='t-69141'>So let's see.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71111' id='t-71111'>So, for instance, we have
a lava lamp application here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='75448' id='t-75448'>Now, you can see,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='77174' id='t-77174'>I can use both of my hands to kind
