<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='108863' id='t-108863'>Chris could be interacting
with another part of Lava,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='111386' id='t-111386'>while I play around with it here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='113044' id='t-113044'>You can imagine
a new kind of sculpting tool,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='115164' id='t-115164'>where I'm kind of warming something up,
making it malleable,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='118167' id='t-118167'>and then letting it cool down
and solidifying in a certain state.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='125712' id='t-125712'>Google should have
something like this in their lobby.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='128683' id='t-128683'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='134000' id='t-134000'>I'll show you a little more
of a concrete example here,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137296' id='t-137296'>as this thing loads.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='139181' id='t-139181'>This is a photographer's
