</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='265341' id='t-265341'>Here's an example of another kind of app.
I can make these little fuzz balls.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='269000' id='t-269000'>It'll remember the strokes I'm making.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='271358' id='t-271358'>Of course I can do it with all my hands.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='273301' id='t-273301'>It's pressure-sensitive.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='275905' id='t-275905'>What's neat about that is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='277485' id='t-277485'>I showed that two-finger gesture
that zooms in really quickly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280474' id='t-280474'>Because you don't have
