<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289076' id='t-289076'>I can create big things out here,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291113' id='t-291113'>but I can go back
and really quickly go back</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293235' id='t-293235'>to where I started,
